For quick compile options type:

 	make help

 ...which gives you:


*********************************** HELP ***********************************

You can set several Makefile variables during invocation of make...

Required?     Description         Variable        Example
--------     -----------------   ------------    ---------------------------------------------
  YES         CDF Library         LIB_CDF         LIB_CDF=/Applications/cdf31-dist/lib/libcdf.a
  YES         CDF Include Files   CDF_INC         CDF_INC=/Applications/cdf31-dist/include/
  NO          C Compiler          CC              CC=gcc
  NO          FORTRAN Compiler    F77             F77=gfortran
  NO          FORTRAN Libraries   FORTRAN_LIB     FORTRAN_LIB=-L/usr/local/lib/x86_64
  NO          IDL Include Files   IDL_INC_DIR     IDL_INC_DIR=/Applications/itt/idl64/external
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Example:

  make CC=gcc F77=gfortran CDF_INC=/Applications/cdf31-dist/include/ LIB_CDF=/Applications/cdf31-dist/lib/libcdf.a IDL_INC_DIR=/Applications/itt/idl64/external

*********************************** HELP ***********************************